parameters:
Auction venue lobby. Right now, the merchandise
prepared by the Imperial Army was in the middle of
a demonstration for the auction.

Hehehe... You understand, don't you? Don't do
anything strange, just quietly flatter the
executives.

If you try anything funny, the bunny ear bomb will
explode and your brains will be mush, you know~
Shut up! I get it! Idiot!

Even so, we've pumped you full of nanomachines
with aphrodisiac effects, so it must be tough just
standing there, huh~?
(It's okay... Shuu will come to rescue me soon...)
Oh? Is this the rare item for this time?
Have this one give a proper greeting!

...I'm Esuka, a former resistance cyborg... I'll
do my best to be a pet that everyone will like
today...
Hohoho. So this is the rumored... let's see.

Oh~ surprisingly soft, aren't you? Were you
dealing with men even in the resistance, hmm?

Hohoho! With such a cute reaction, it seems there
were no worthy men in the resistance, huh?
Hmm, I want to see more reactions, bring the toy.
Hey, hurry up and bring it over.

The rule is to choose and bring three types of
goods by yourself.
Hohoho! So, Esuka-chan likes this sort of thing~

I... I only brought them because you told me
to...!
Then, shall we try them out now?
Fufufu, you don't have to hold back, you know.
Hohoho, that's right, it's good to moan honestly.

Oh, I see you're already at it. May I give it a
try as well?
Well, well, long time no see, General.

Hahaha, she's caused us quite a bit of trouble.
I've been wanting to get my hands on her for a
while now.

Oh, it seems we've got ourselves a formidable
opponent.

Hehehe, but even if we get our hands on her, it's
troublesome to discipline her if she's too
defiant.

Don't worry, we'll make sure to train her into a
submissive female before we deliver her.

Hahaha! What's this, already at your limit? Make
sure to appeal properly so a kind person will buy
you.
(N-No... Not in front of these lowlifes...)

Hohoho, how disgraceful in public. This seems like
it's going to be quite a task to discipline her.

Well, isn't she quite adorable? I'd like to make
her cry out shamelessly every night under my
command.

Hahaha, there are still many customers to come.
Make sure to appeal properly.

The man called the general puts a price tag on
Esuka. The auction starts from the highest price
on the tag.
Oh, so this is the Resistance's cyborg?
Let me have a try as well.

Ladies and gentlemen, the auction will soon
commence. Please make your way to the venue.

Ugh, this is terrible. Well, she's the main
attraction this time around.

Gyahahaha, it looks like you're going to fetch a
high price, Esuka-chan. Make sure to liven up the
auction for us.
